<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA523_04_IH_0002_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema523_04.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema523_04_ih_0002">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y">선대칭도형을 모두 찾아 기호를 골라 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box align_center justify_center dir_col">
          <div class="img_area">
            <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA523_04_IH/0002_01.png" alt="" />
            <div class="boolean_wrap">
              <button class="button1" data-answer-single="true">가</button>
              <button class="button2" data-answer-single="true">나</button>
              <button class="button3" data-answer-single="false">다</button>
              <button class="button4" data-answer-single="true">라</button>
              <button class="button5" data-answer-single="false">마</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">한 직선을 따라 접었을 때 완전히 겹치는 도형은 가, 나, 라입니다.</p>
                <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA523_04_IH/0002_02.png" alt="" />
                <p class="text_label">
                  <span class="label reference">참고</span>
                  <span lang="y"> 선대칭도형을 찾을 때에는 대칭축을 세로뿐만 아니라 가로, 대각선 등 여러 방향으로 생각합니다. </span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
